<div class="guide-main-content">

<p class="guide-intro">Outreach is the enterprise standard for sales engagement platforms. At approximately $100–$140/user/month, it offers deep Salesforce integration, AI deal intelligence, pipeline forecasting, and the most mature SDR sequencing workflow in the category. But Outreach is not the right choice for every team — it is expensive, complex to administer, and overkill for teams under 20 seats. Here are the 6 best alternatives, ranked by use case.</p>

<h2>When to Consider an Outreach Alternative</h2>

