<thead>
<tr><th>If Your Priority Is...</th><th>Better Alternative</th><th>Why</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>AE deal management and forecasting</td><td>Salesloft</td><td>Salesloft's deal management is stronger for full-cycle AEs</td></tr>
<tr><td>Budget under $100/user/month</td><td>Apollo.io</td><td>Apollo at $49–99/user/mo includes data + engagement in one</td></tr>
<tr><td>CRM-native (HubSpot shop)</td><td>HubSpot Sales Hub</td><td>Eliminates a separate SEP subscription for HubSpot users</td></tr>
<tr><td>AI-native engagement (built AI-first)</td><td>Regie.ai</td><td>Regie.ai was built AI-first; Outreach bolted AI onto legacy platform</td></tr>
<tr><td>Cold email only (no enterprise workflow)</td><td>Instantly.ai or Smartlead</td><td>10x cheaper, better deliverability for pure cold email</td></tr>
<tr><td>Team under 10 seats</td><td>Apollo.io or HubSpot</td><td>Outreach's complexity and cost are not justified at small scale</td></tr>
</tbody>
